Presiding Chairman Carlos Roman L. Uybarreta instructed the Committee Secretariat to invite to the next hearing the ERC, MERALCO, Union of Local Authorities of the Philippines (ULAP) and other LGU groups and the PNOC-Renewable Corporation.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp3. Referred to the Technical Working Group (TWG) on 2018-09-10</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON ENERGY ON 2018-01-17</td></tr></table>